verbose_text: Nutlin-3 stabilized p53 protein levels but was not able to rescue the reduction of p53 in response to PHD3 knockdown or inhibition, confirming that the functional MDM2 and PHD3 act independently of each other (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A).
